# UX reference assets

- The Bills main screen design reference is **`Bills_Main.png`** (typically under `UX_Reference` or the project’s reference image folder).
- Whenever **`Bills_Main.jpg`** or another **`.jpg`** path is mentioned for a UX/screenshot asset, **fall back to the same basename with `.png`** (e.g. `Bills_Main.png`) and use that file if present.
